suffering in the shadows.

47:33.114 --> 47:34.548
I don't believe in shadows.

47:34.582 --> 47:37.684
I believe
in the light of scientific inquiry.

47:37.718 --> 47:41.788
I believe I have
a responsibility to those men,

47:41.822 --> 47:46.426
whether they're salesmen
or lawyers...

47:46.460 --> 47:50.797
or a provost of a major university.

47:56.637 --> 47:58.672
[ Sighs ]

48:00.675 --> 48:03.677
I'm begging you to reconsider.

48:03.711 --> 48:06.947
If not for my sake,

48:06.981 --> 48:10.483
then for those men in the shadows.

48:10.518 --> 48:13.119
BARTON:
What the hell is this, Bill?

48:14.722 --> 48:16.957
WILLIAM:
It's a necessary evil.

48:26.100 --> 48:28.569
BARTON:
Thought you'd gone AWOL.

48:29.036 --> 48:32.572
WILLIAM:
Uh, I'm not much for goodbye parties.

48:32.607 --> 48:33.873
BARTON:
[ Chuckles ]

48:33.908 --> 48:36.444
