they ever interviewed...

49:19.553 --> 49:22.856
A smug, self-satisfied horse's ass.

49:22.890 --> 49:25.592
- WILLIAM: Ah.
- BARTON: Yeah, "we can't take him

49:25.626 --> 49:28.528
