a separate wing for his ego"...

49:28.562 --> 49:31.364
Something like that.

49:31.399 --> 49:33.533
- WILLIAM: I see.
- BARTON: [ Chuckles ]

49:33.567 --> 49:38.104
I, uh, I told Dean Young
he could take us both,

49:38.139 --> 49:41.007
or he could take the provost job
and shove it.

49:43.244 --> 49:46.212
So meet me in St. Louis?

49:52.019 --> 49:56.289
[ Chuckles ]
Bill...

